## Policy Format Standard

Every policy in this portfolio follows this professional structure:

| Section | What It Contains |
|---|---|
| **1. Purpose** | Why the policy exists and what it protects |
| **2. Scope** | Who and what the policy applies to |
| **3. Policy Statements** | The actual rules and requirements |
| **4. Prohibited Activities** | Explicit list of what is not allowed |
| **5. Responsibilities** | Who owns, enforces, and complies with the policy |
| **6. Enforcement** | Consequences for non-compliance |
| **7. Review Cycle** | How often the policy is reviewed and updated |
| **8. Version History** | Document change log with dates and approver |

