## PWD-001 — Password Policy

**SOC 2 Mapping:** CC6.6 — Logical Access through Transmission Mediums
**Purpose:** Establish minimum password standards to protect system access

**Key Requirements:**

| Requirement | Standard |
|---|---|
| Minimum length | 12 characters |
| Complexity | Uppercase + lowercase + number + special character |
| Rotation period | Every 90 days for privileged accounts; 180 days for standard |
| Password reuse | Last 12 passwords cannot be reused |
| MFA | Required for all remote access and privileged accounts |
| Shared accounts | Prohibited — every user must have a unique credential |
| Password manager | Recommended for all employees |
| Failed login lockout | Account locked after 5 consecutive failed attempts |

